## Workflow

<!-- How you want Claude to work here. Keep it short — the detailed procedures
     live in skills, not in this file. -->

- Default loop: explore → plan → code → verify. Plan before editing non-trivial changes.
- Build features and fix bugs test-first — use the `tdd` skill.
- For hard/slow bugs, use the `diagnosing-bugs` skill (build a failing repro first).
- Always end a change by running the test suite and the linter before declaring done.
